OL,3,C'We're devastated': Minibus stolen
OL,4,Cfrom autism charity
OL,6,FStaff at an autism charity have been
OL,7,Fleft "devastated" after thieves stole
OL,8,Fa custom-made minibus from one of its
OL,9,Fresidential homes.
OL,11,FThe eight-seater van was taken on
OL,12,FFriday 2 February from the North East
OL,13,FAutism Society (NEAS) home in
OL,14,FSunderland, where two autistic men
OL,15,Fwith complex needs live with a team of
OL,16,Fcarers.
