OL,6,FStaff added that the minibus was vital
OL,7,Ffor medical appointments and
OL,8,Femergencies, trips out, visits to
OL,9,Ffamilies, and holidays, both for the
OL,10,Ftwo men and for autistic children
OL,11,Fliving in nearby NEAS homes.
OL,13,FThe home's manager, Robyn Beecroft,
OL,14,Fsaid: "I'm devastated that somebody
OL,15,Fwould go out of their way to take
OL,16,Fsomething so important to vulnerable
OL,17,Fpeople.
