OL,6,F"The minibus had a blue badge and
OL,7,Fcontained safety and sensory equipment
OL,8,Fsuch as weighted blankets that
OL,9,Fresidents could use on journeys. It
OL,10,Fwas obvious who it was for.
OL,12,F"What kind of a person would do this?
OL,13,FIt's disgusting."
OL,15,FThe van was a blue Ford Tourneo Custom
OL,16,Fand cost more than #41,500.
