OL,3,C'We're devastated': Minibus stolen
OL,4,Cfrom autism charity
OL,6,FBecause it was custom-made for the
OL,7,Fcharity, staff have said there is a 10-
OL,8,Fmonth wait for a new one, and they are
OL,9,Fhaving to rent a van daily because the
OL,10,Fhome can't do without it.
OL,12,FMs Beecroft said: "The two residents
OL,13,Frely on the van to be able to go out
OL,14,For get to medicalJappointments. We use
OL,15,Fit for day trips and holidays.
