OL,6,FA Northumbria Police spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "We received a report that a
OL,8,Fvehicle was stolen from outside an
OL,9,Faddress on Woodstock Avenue, in the
OL,10,FGrangetown area of Sunderland,
OL,11,Fsometime between 9pm on Thursday 1
OL,12,FFebruary and 12pm on Friday 2
OL,13,FFebruary."
OL,15,FAnyone with any information is urged
OL,16,Fto contact Northumbria Police via the
OL,17,F"Report" page of the website or call
OL,18,F101, quoting crime reference number
OL,19,F13353P/24.
